OL,3,CGrooming gangs hearings in Scottish
OL,4,CChild Abuse Inquiry to begin next year
OL,6,FThe Scottish Child Abuse Inquiry will
OL,7,Fexamine grooming gangs and the
OL,8,Ffailures of institutions to protect
OL,9,Fchildren in care when a new phase
OL,10,Fbegins.
OL,12,FLady Smith's inquiry, which began in
OL,13,F2015, will focus on the exploitation
OL,14,Fof children who were in care at the
OL,15,Ftime of the abuse.
OL,17,FThis could include grooming or
OL,18,Fexploitation which took place outside
OL,19,Fthe child's placement or foster home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
