OL,3,CGrooming gangs hearings in Scottish
OL,4,CChild Abuse Inquiry to begin next year
OL,6,FIn February, the Scottish Government
OL,7,Fordered a separate inquiry into
OL,8,Fgrooming gangs north of the border
OL,9,Fwith "full investigatory powers", to
OL,10,Fbe chaired by Professor Alexis Jay.
OL,12,FPhase 11 of Lady Smith's inquiry will
OL,13,Fbe titled "Protecting children in care
OL,14,Fin Scotland from abuse: present and
OL,15,Ffuture".
OL,17,FClosing submissions in Phase 10 of the
OL,18,Finquiry will begin on Thursday.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@`O]uD@KOUwD@GO]
