OL,3,CGrooming gangs hearings in Scottish
OL,4,CChild Abuse Inquiry to begin next year
OL,6,FDescribing the next phase, Lady Smith
OL,7,Fsaid it will examine whether
OL,8,Fgovernment and other institutions
OL,9,Ffailed to protect children from abuse.
OL,11,FPhase 11 will begin later in 2026,
OL,12,Fwith the section on child exploitation
OL,13,Fstarting in early 2027.She said: "The
OL,14,Fstructure of Phase 11 hearings will
OL,15,Falso allow for some specific themes to
OL,16,Fbe explored.
OL,18,F"For example, later this year we will
OL,19,Fconsider 'Why children abuse other
OL,20,Fchildren'.
OL,26,@uD@bOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781743669
OL,3,CGrooming gangs hearings in Scottish
OL,4,CChild Abuse Inquiry to begin next year
OL,6,F"Also, I recently made an announcement
OL,7,Fin relation to our work regarding the
OL,8,Fexploitation of children in care and
OL,9,Fwe plan to include it in our
OL,10,Fpresentation of Phase 11.
OL,12,F"By exploitation, I mean a type of
OL,13,Fabuse in which a single person or
OL,14,Fgroups of people persuade or force a
OL,15,Fchild to engage in sexual or other
OL,16,Factivity.
OL,18,F"When groups of people do this, they
OL,19,Fmay be referred to as 'grooming gangs'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781743669
OL,3,CGrooming gangs hearings in Scottish
OL,4,CChild Abuse Inquiry to begin next year
OL,6,F"So long as the exploited child was in
OL,7,Fcare, we can investigate the abuse
OL,8,Feven if the grooming or the
OL,9,Fexploitation took place outside the
OL,10,Fplacement or foster home.
OL,12,F"And, we can investigate allegations
OL,13,Fof abuse which happened before the end
OL,14,Fof December 2014 and, to be clear, we
OL,15,Fcan investigate abuse which began
OL,16,Fbefore and continued after that date.
OL,18,F"We plan to focus on the exploitation
OL,19,Fof children in care in our Phase 11
OL,20,Fhearings in the early part of 2027."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@dO]
